{"tid":2035300,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊持續投資遊戲業 成日本Marvelous最大股東","createTime":"2020-05-25T21:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T21:39:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0285d7f9db05d956173eec9efdef96de912368","tid":2035300,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:14:07.000Z","msg":"〔 財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國網路巨頭騰訊持續投資遊戲公司，其最新一步為以約70億日圓（約新台幣19.7億元），收購日本遊戲開發商Marvelous達20％的股份，成為Marvelous最大股東，專家指出，騰訊之所以投資Marvelous，可能旨在向日本公司學習如何製作主機（如PS4、Xbox、任天堂Switch）遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》今（25）報導，中國騰訊將透過關聯公司Image Frame Investment，以約70億日圓收購日本遊戲開發商Marvelous達20％的股份。Marvelous將以每股576日圓出售862萬股新股，股東Amuse Capital和Nakayama Hayao，則將分別以相同價格出售283萬股和70.86萬股。<br />\n<br />\nMarvelous則將利用騰訊的投資持續經營現有IP，和在未來3年推出新IP，該遊戲公司目前的知名作品，則為牧場物語系列 （Story of Seasons）和機甲戰魔（Deamon X Machina）等。<br />\n<br />\nAce研究所（Ace Research Institute）分析師Hideki Yasuda指出，騰訊投資Marvelous的目的，可能是為了向日本公司學習如何製作主機遊戲，同時得到投資的Marvelous公司，則能渡過全球經濟的不確定性時期，並向西方市場發行更多該公司在日本國內受歡迎的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n目前，騰訊已和Marvelous開始合作開發遊戲IP。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，騰訊握有遊戲商Epic Games達48.4%的股份；魁匠團（Bluehole）為知名大逃殺遊戲《絕地求生》（PUBG）開發商，由騰訊持股11.5％，並有權在中國發行PUBG；開發《英雄聯盟》（League of Legends）的Riot Games是騰訊100持股的子公司；騰訊另對長紅遊戲《刺客教條》系列發行商Ubisoft，和動視暴雪各持股5%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3176890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3176890&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=9d7ad1cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3176890&h=218dae1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3176890</a>"},{"pid":"04a0a335b095ec62a32ce23c185515a9037ef6f2","tid":2035300,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:16:42.000Z","msg":"唔好沉迷二次元喇<br />\n面對現實番黎三次元<br />\n<br />\n香港需要肥宅做軍武宅"},{"pid":"c50e5fd5ea275c18a246613d9c90fb86b2a76d9b","tid":2035300,"uid":16878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:36:43.000Z","msg":"以後無得玩牧場物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08754415c4fe3572653e440657182ebb59bd61fe","tid":2035300,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c50e5fd5ea275c18a246613d9c90fb86b2a76d9b","tid":2035300,"uid":16878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T21:36:43.000Z","msg":"以後無得玩牧場物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:38:55.000Z","msg":"會有「牧场物语」"},{"pid":"854b0d798c6ed0688c54c868f407e6d3da47a74f","tid":2035300,"uid":243380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"佢買咩廠我就唔玩咩game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43900364bd1de743c28d181e384f41a16ba8cc5d","tid":2035300,"uid":201025,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"854b0d798c6ed0688c54c868f407e6d3da47a74f","tid":2035300,"uid":243380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"佢買咩廠我就唔玩咩game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T20:29:56.000Z","msg":"我驚你遲早要玩window 接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c53af0c508c8e2ecb37d8c85990fdc0d461c5e1","tid":2035300,"uid":28131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"854b0d798c6ed0688c54c868f407e6d3da47a74f","tid":2035300,"uid":243380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"佢買咩廠我就唔玩咩game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T21:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死人玩彈珠台"},{"pid":"0ce7a9b2329c78ea78a27d32a43365f8ac270965","tid":2035300,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0